 51, 51);font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"><br/></span></strong></p><p data-end=\"259\" data-start=\"114\" style='font-style: normal;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75em;vertical-align: bottom;text-decoration: none;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;'><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">周一美股尾盘，运动服饰零售商 Lululemon 股价上涨1.4%，但股价的短暂回升，难以掩盖公司内部正酝酿的一场罕见权力斗争，创始人、重要股东 Chip Wilson 正公开挑战现任董事会，要求在遴选下一任首席执行官之前，对董事会进行重组。</span></p><p data-end=\"259\" data-start=\"114\" style='font-style: normal;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75em;vertical-align: bottom;text-decoration: none;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;'><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"><br/></span></p><p data-end=\"455\" data-start=\"261\" style='font-style: normal;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75em;vertical-align: bottom;text-decoration: none;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;'><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">根据披露，Wilson 已在即将于2026年召开的年度股东大会上，正式提名三名新的董事候选人，分别为前 On Holding 联合首席执行官 Marc Maurer、前 ESPN 首席营销官 Laura Gentile，以及前动视首席执行官 Eric Hirshberg。</span></p><p data-end=\"455\" data-start=\"261\" style='font-style: normal;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75em;vertical-align: bottom;text-decoration: none;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;'><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"><br/></span></p><p data-end=\"455\" data-start=\"261\" style='font-style: normal;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75em;vertical-align: bottom;text-decoration: none;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;'><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">这三位候选人均拥有深厚的品牌、产品或内容型消费公司管理经验，与现任董事会成员构成明显差异。</span></p><p data-end=\"455\" data-start=\"261\" style='font-style: normal;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75em;vertical-align: bottom;text-decoration: none;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;'><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"><br/></span></p><p data-end=\"494\" data-start=\"457\" style='font-style: normal;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75em;vertical-align: bottom;text-decoration: none;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;'><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">这一步骤，被外界普遍解读为 Wilson 对当前董事会运营能力的直接否定。</span></p><p data-end=\"494\" data-start=\"457\" style='font-style: normal;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75em;vertical-align: bottom;text-decoration: none;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;'><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\"><br/></span></p><p data-end=\"605\" data-start=\"496\" style='font-style: normal;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: 0.544px;orphans: 2;text-align: justify;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;caret-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75em;vertical-align: bottom;text-decoration: none;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;'><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">在周一发布的声明中，Wilson直言不讳地批评称，近期的首席执行官更迭公告，已经是董事会在监督职责上的第三次彻底失职，他指出，董事会至今未能提出清晰、可信的CEO继任计划，而这正是公司在关键转型期最致命的漏洞。</span></p><p data-end=\"605\" data-start=\"496\" style='font-style: normal;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-family: \"PingFang SC\", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: nor